text: Georg Agrikola (born 11 January 1959) is a German rower. He competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics and the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:German male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of West Germany Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:People from Landau
